176
00:09:45,620 --> 00:09:49,010
Hobak, is there anything we can do?

177
00:09:53,230 --> 00:09:55,640
Is there anything, Minjung?

178
00:09:58,860 --> 00:10:02,380
Oh, so there isn't.

179
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:03,940
What will we do?

180
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:06,650
