190
00:10:27,460 --> 00:10:29,950
- Get ready for my funeral.
- You can't!

191
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,890
- Mom!
- Mother.

192
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:43,840
My wife.

193
00:10:43,860 --> 00:10:46,090
I think I married well.

194
00:10:46,100 --> 00:10:47,790
You do?

195
00:10:47,790 --> 00:10:50,040
My mom.

196
00:10:50,050 --> 00:10:53,110
