209
00:11:54,790 --> 00:11:56,040
Designer handbags.

210
00:11:56,050 --> 00:11:57,280
Besides that.

211
00:11:57,290 --> 00:11:59,340
- Money.
- Jangbi!

212
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:01,490
I'm serious.

213
