220
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:42,540
I'm your husband's mother.
Your mother in law.

221
00:12:42,550 --> 00:12:44,440
You don't get it?

222
00:12:44,460 --> 00:12:48,490
You think I came all the way here to get a measly $5,000?

223
00:12:49,330 --> 00:12:52,350
You think I'm that easy?

224
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:56,010
You think you can get away with $5,000?

225
00:12:56,020 --> 00:13:01,040
