229
00:13:08,290 --> 00:13:10,910
It's not like that, mother.

230
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:15,490
I don't understand why you're doing this.

231
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:17,320
Why can't you understand?

232
00:13:17,330 --> 00:13:19,190
You must be really stupid.

233
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:21,950
This couldn't be any simpler.

234
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:25,240
How did you teach your students?

235
00:13:25,250 --> 00:13:27,540
You're a college graduate!

236
00:13:27,550 --> 00:13:30,040
How can you be so dumb?

237
00:13:30,050 --> 00:13:34,010
Mother, you can say anything you want,

238
00:13:34,020 --> 00:13:37,740
but if you want Sangnam and me to be happy,

239
00:13:37,750 --> 00:13:40,990
I don't get why you would do this to me.

240
00:13:41,730 --> 00:13:45,090
I guess you don't want this.

241
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:49,740
When will you give me the rest?

242
00:13:49,750 --> 00:13:51,540
I can't give you anymore.

243
00:13:52,290 --> 00:13:53,380
What?

244
00:13:53,390 --> 00:13:57,720
