248
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:07,010
But I gave you $5,000 behind his back.

249
00:14:07,020 --> 00:14:09,010
And I gave you another $5,000.

250
00:14:09,020 --> 00:14:10,680
That's $10,000.

251
00:14:10,700 --> 00:14:13,920
For me, that's a lot of money.

252
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:15,490
I can't give you anymore.

253
00:14:15,500 --> 00:14:18,090
You're pretty bold.

254
00:14:18,100 --> 00:14:21,690
Which tea house did you work at?

255
00:14:21,700 --> 00:14:24,690
