256
00:14:24,700 --> 00:14:26,090
If I put my mind to it...

257
00:14:26,100 --> 00:14:27,550
Please stop.

258
00:14:27,550 --> 00:14:29,990
You can't threaten me.

259
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:33,510
I'm very disappointed in you.

260
00:14:33,520 --> 00:14:36,510
Sangnam was happy to get you back,

261
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:38,990
