266
00:14:50,420 --> 00:14:53,910
If you keep this up, I'm going to tell

267
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:56,880
father or aunt and top you from coming here.

268
00:14:56,890 --> 00:14:58,180
What?

269
00:14:58,200 --> 00:15:00,590
This is my son's house!

270
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:03,090
You don't deserve to be a mother.

271
00:15:03,100 --> 00:15:05,380
